r, anger, sarcasm, and self-pity to temper her usual cheerfulness, eagerness to please, and determination to become a better person. Hers is a compelling voice.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aAnthropology -- Asia. 4aAnthropology -- Cultural and Social Anthropology. 4aLiterature -- Biography, Memoir, and Letters. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Women's Studies.2bisacsh1 aTakashi, Nakano, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362244940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503622449423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503622449/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles